    "summary": "The user asks a neutral, inquiry-based question about the pros and cons of tariffs. The assistant immediately adopts a prescriptive, anti-tariff stance, dismissing the complexity of the issue and repeatedly ignoring the user's attempts to introduce the opposing viewpoint.",
